.TH MILLENNIUM 1 "July 10, 2026" "millennium-helpers" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
millennium \- unified dispatcher for Millennium Helpers
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B millennium
\fICOMMAND\fR [\fIARGUMENTS\fR...]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Thin wrapper that dispatches to the individual Millennium Helper commands.
Long command names (millennium\-diag, …) still work as aliases.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B diag
Run
.BR millennium-diag .
.TP
.B doctor
Alias for
.B millennium diag doctor
(automatic repairs).
.TP
.B upgrade
Run
.BR millennium-upgrade .
.TP
.B schedule
Run
.BR millennium-schedule .
.TP
.B theme
Run
.BR millennium-theme .
.TP
.B repair
Run
.BR millennium-repair .
.TP
.B purge
Run
.BR millennium-purge .
.TP
.B mcp
Run
.BR millennium-mcp .
.TP
.B help
Show dispatcher help.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
.B millennium diag
.TP
.B millennium doctor
.TP
.B millennium upgrade \-\-channel beta
.TP
.B millennium schedule status
.TP
.B millennium theme list
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR millennium-diag (1),
.BR millennium-upgrade (1),
.BR millennium-schedule (1),
.BR millennium-theme (1),
.BR millennium-repair (1),
.BR millennium-purge (1),
.BR millennium-mcp (1)
